Reminder: Document Awaiting Your Signature

Hello <%= @signature_request.signer_display_name %>,

This is a friendly reminder that <%= @signature_request.requester.full_name %> is waiting for your signature on a document.

Document: <%= @document.name %>
From: <%= @signature_request.requester.full_name %>
<% if @signature_request.expires_at.present? -%>
Expires: <%= @signature_request.expires_at.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %>
<% end -%>
<% if @signature_request.message.present? %>
"<%= @signature_request.message %>"
<% end %>
Review and sign your document:
<%= @signing_url %>
